# Tipos de datos: Matrices

#### Multiplicaci칩n

.pull-left[
```{r}
x <- c(7,7,3,4,2,6,3,1,2)
z <- matrix(x, nrow = 3, ncol = 3)
z
```
]

.pull-right[
```{r}
x <- c(1,5,6,7,3,3,1,2,1)
n <- matrix(x, nrow = 3, ncol = 3)
n
```
]

```{r}
z %*% n
```

