# Tipos de datos: Matrices

#### Resoluci칩n de ecuaciones

$$\begin{array} {lcl} 3x+2y & = & 8 \\ x + y& = & 2 \end{array}$$


.pull-left[
```{r}
a <- matrix(c(3,1,2,1),nrow=2,ncol=2)
a
```
]

.pull-right[
```{r}
b <- matrix(c(8,2),nrow=2,ncol=1)
b
```
]

```{r}
solve(a,b)
```

